INSERT INTO `letters` VALUES (3,'My Second Letter','I wrote this for ivan.','2025-11-11 16:34:12',1,2,0,0),(4,'Ivan First Letter','My dearest,\nYou are the gentle sunrise to my restless nights, the calm in the middle of my storms. With every word you speak, you write poetry on my heart. With every touch, you paint color into my ordinary days. Loving you feels like discovering a new world—one filled with warmth, laughter, and endless tenderness. I’m grateful that in this lifetime, our souls found each other.','2025-11-11 16:41:38',2,1,0,0),(5,'Ivan Second Letter','To the one who holds my heart,\nI’ve met many people in my life, but no one has ever made me feel the way you do. You understand me in ways I didn’t know were possible. You see the parts of me that I keep hidden, and still, you choose to stay. Your love makes me brave. Your presence makes me whole. I want to continue choosing you—today, tomorrow, and all the days after.','2025-11-11 17:01:17',2,1,0,0),(6,'Ivan Third Letter Test','My love,\nEvery day with you feels like a quiet miracle. Even in moments when we’re apart, my heart finds its way back to you—like it always does. You bring peace to my chaos and warmth to every cold corner of my life. I don’t need grand things or perfect days; I just need you. Thank you for being my favorite feeling.','2025-11-11 17:01:46',2,1,0,0),(7,'My First Letter','I wrote this for ivan','2025-11-11 17:02:44',1,2,1,0),(8,'My Third Letter','I wrote this for ivan.','2025-11-16 12:26:12',1,2,0,0),(12,'Short but Heart-Meltings','Love,\nI don’t say this enough, but you are everything to me. You make life brighter, lighter, and more beautiful without even trying. I’m thankful for you today and every day after. I love you—simply, deeply, endlessly.','2025-11-16 15:24:37',2,1,0,0),(14,'Long, Passionate & Intense','My beloved,\nThere are so many things I want to tell you, and yet words feel too small for the way I feel. Every moment I spend with you leaves a mark on me—your touch, your voice, your thoughts, your kindness. You have become the fire that keeps me warm, the heartbeat that steadies me, the feeling I never want to lose.\n\nYou fill my days with meaning and my nights with longing. I find myself thinking of you at random moments: when I wake up, when I’m tired, when I hear a song, when something reminds me of you. Every thought leads me back to the same realization—I am deeply, undeniably in love with you.\n\nI choose you not because I need to, but because my heart does. And I will continue choosing you in every sunrise and every sunset, in every quiet moment and every storm. There is no one else I want, no one else I dream of, no one else my heart beats for the way it beats for you.','2025-11-16 16:11:33',1,2,1,0),(15,'ELON','test eloom','2025-11-16 16:46:14',3,1,1,0),(16,'I am Elon','Test','2025-11-16 16:47:02',1,3,0,0),(17,'My Third Letter','I wrote this for ivan.','2025-11-18 21:59:42',1,1,1,0),(18,'Test letter','test for is_public.','2025-11-18 22:01:53',1,2,1,0),(19,'Test letter','Ako lng to','2025-11-18 22:02:15',1,2,1,0),(20,'is public','public test','2025-11-19 11:33:10',NULL,1,1,0),(21,'Elon Public Letter','ahahhaha\n\nwdknqewdinq\nwldmqewkpdnqendeqpfepfnadfndkfnkdlsnffdsfdsfknsdkfnkdslksdnflksfnff\nadfknsdkfnskdnflksdfklsdfnsdnkv\nalmamaosdmasdoamdmasoasmc[asmcmo[aso[csac\nacklasnclknaclknakncalncacnkandnacnacnadcnakcknakncankc\nasknaslkcnacknanckacnac;aknklkcnakcnakc;ancakxcnak\nacalknckanclkannclkn','2025-11-19 12:18:02',8,3,1,0),(22,'. “The Reason I Wake Up Smiling”','My love,\nEvery day I wake up grateful that the universe found a way to cross our paths. You have this incredible ability to make even the quiet moments feel meaningful, as if simply existing beside you is enough to make the world feel lighter. I never believed someone could bring both peace and excitement into my life at the same time, but you do that without even trying. Thank you for loving me in ways I never thought I deserved. I hope you know that my heart chooses you, in every moment, in every version of the future I imagine.','2025-11-19 12:46:21',8,7,1,0),(23,'You Live in My Smile','My dearest,\nSometimes I find myself smiling for no reason, and then I realize it’s because of you. You’ve woven yourself into my days so naturally that everything I do now feels touched by your presence. I love the way you support me, how you listen, how you understand even the things I don’t say out loud. You’ve become my comfort, my strength, and my soft place to fall. I want to spend my life showing you the same warmth you give so effortlessly.','2025-11-19 12:47:07',8,7,1,0),(24,'If You Saw Yourself Through My Eyes','My sweetheart,\nI love you in all the ways I know how — in my words, in my actions, in the moments where I hold you close, and even in the silence where all I can do is look at you and hope you understand how deeply you are cherished. You bring warmth into places inside me that I didn’t realize were cold. You make me want to become a better person, not out of pressure, but because your love inspires me. Every day with you feels like a blessing I don’t take for granted.','2025-11-19 12:47:33',3,7,1,0),(25,'You’re the One I Share My World With','My love,\nYou have this way of making me feel chosen, not by chance or convenience, but intentionally — and that means more to me than you could ever imagine. I love how your presence feels like home, how your voice grounds me, and how your love teaches me patience and understanding. You’re the story I never get tired of telling myself, the comfort I search for, and the dream I want to protect. I hope I give you the same warmth you give me every day.','2025-11-19 12:48:01',3,7,1,0),(26,'ou’re the One I Share My World With','o the love of my life,\nYou’re the person I want to share my secrets with, my small victories, my silly stories, and my quiet fears. You’ve become someone I can’t imagine life without, not because I depend on you, but because you make life so much more meaningful. I love how you bring color to my gray days and calm to my stormy ones. Thank you for being gentle with my heart and strong for it when I can’t be.','2025-11-19 12:49:43',NULL,5,1,0),(27,'Long, Passionate & Intense','Sweetheart,\nI used to think love was supposed to be loud — grand gestures, dramatic moments, overwhelming emotions. But then you came along and showed me the beauty of quiet love: the gentle touches, the soft words, the steady presence that never wavers. You make my life feel balanced and whole. I love that I can be myself with you — messy, confused, imperfect — and still feel adored. You are my heart’s favorite place to rest.','2025-11-19 12:50:04',NULL,5,1,0),(28,'The Beauty of Quiet Love','Sweetheart,\nI used to think love was supposed to be loud — grand gestures, dramatic moments, overwhelming emotions. But then you came along and showed me the beauty of quiet love: the gentle touches, the soft words, the steady presence that never wavers. You make my life feel balanced and whole. I love that I can be myself with you — messy, confused, imperfect — and still feel adored. You are my heart’s favorite place to rest.','2025-11-19 12:50:34',2,5,1,0),(29,'“The Kind of Love That Lasts”','eloved,\nWhen I think about love, I think about you. Not the dramatic, movie kind of love — but the real, steady, gentle kind that grows deeper with time. You make me feel safe, valued, and genuinely seen. With you, I don’t feel the need to pretend or hide parts of myself. You accept me with all my flaws, and somehow you still look at me like I’m something extraordinary. I carry that feeling with me everywhere I go.','2025-11-19 12:51:12',5,5,1,0),(30,'“If You Saw Yourself Through My Eyes”','My heart,\nI wish you could see yourself through my eyes — the kindness you give, the strength you hold, the quiet beauty that blooms from your soul. You are more than enough, more than wonderful, more than anything I ever dreamed I would find in this lifetime. Being with you makes life feel softer, kinder, more hopeful. Thank you for loving me, trusting me, and choosing me. I promise to keep choosing you too.','2025-11-19 12:52:19',7,6,1,0),(31,'“You Live in My Smile”','y dearest,\nSometimes I find myself smiling for no reason, and then I realize it’s because of you. You’ve woven yourself into my days so naturally that everything I do now feels touched by your presence. I love the way you support me, how you listen, how you understand even the things I don’t say out loud. You’ve become my comfort, my strength, and my soft place to fall. I want to spend my life showing you the same warmth you give so effortlessly.','2025-11-19 12:52:40',4,6,1,0),(32,'Lucius ','Test ni lucius ivan','2025-11-19 18:21:43',10,9,1,0),(33,'Hello Babe Goodbye','Dear Babe Arn,\n\nI hope you can finally breathe now, babe.\nI understand now why you needed space and time for yourself. I\'m sorry for the things I did that you didn\'t like, babe. I honestly wasn\'t aware. I should\'ve apologized when you told me, instead of giving you solutions and excuses. That was my mistake.\n\nI didn\'t realize that I had made you my whole world, and expecting you to do the same or to reciprocate that might have put too much pressure on you. I forgot to give you your own time, time for yourself, your family, and your friends. I know this realization came late, babe, and maybe if we hadn\'t cooled off, I wouldn\'t have realized all these things.\n\nI\'m sorry if I was too much without even realizing it. I just hope that when you can finally breathe, when you\'ve given yourself the time I took away from you, you can somehow find your way back to me. I\'m here for you, always.\n\nIt\'s okay to feel lost, babe. I didn\'t realize that sometimes we really need to breathe in order to grow. This trip made me realize a lot, and it helped me understand you more.\n\nMessage me when you\'re ready, babe. No rush. \'ll be right here, waiting.\n\nFeel free to modify this message. Is there anything you may want to add?','2025-11-19 18:43:05',NULL,11,1,0),(34,'My first ever AI letter','Dear [Name],\n\nI hope this note finds you well. I’m writing to admit a small but embarrassing blunder of mine: in the rush of the day, I mistakenly sent you a photo of my cat wearing a sombrero instead of the spreadsheet you needed. I understand how essential that budget analysis is to our work, and I’m truly sorry for the unintended “fashion show” in our correspondence.\n\nPlease know that I’ve taken this as a lesson in double‑checking everything before I hit send. I promise there will be no more feline wardrobe mishaps in our professional exchanges.\n\nThank you for your patience, your sense of humor, and the warmth you bring to our collaboration. If there’s anything else I can do to make amends for this slip, just let me know—I’ll ensure that only my oversight ends up “in the doghouse,” not our project’s timeline.\n\nWith sincere apologies and a heartfelt virtual high‑five for the moment of levity we shared,\n\nWarmest regards,\n\n[Your Name]','2025-11-20 18:31:15',3,10,1,0),(35,'Test Label','Dear Maya,\n\nI hope this note finds you surrounded by warmth and the gentle hum of everyday life. I’ve been thinking about our recent conversation and felt compelled to write to you, just to let you know how much your friendship means to me.\n\nYou have a remarkable way of turning ordinary moments into something memorable. Whether it’s your infectious laugh or the quiet comfort you offer when I need a listening ear, you bring light into my days. I cherish the countless memories we’ve shared—from late‑night coffee chats to spontaneous road trips—and I’m grateful for every laugh, tear, and quiet silence that has deepened our bond.\n\nI want you to know that I’m here for you, just as you’ve always been for me. If you ever need a shoulder to lean on, a partner in adventure, or simply someone to share a cup of tea with, I’ll be there. Your resilience, kindness, and unwavering optimism inspire me to be a better version of myself, and for that, I thank you from the bottom of my heart.\n\nWith warmest wishes and a heartfelt hug,\n\nSam','2025-11-20 18:44:55',9,10,1,1),(36,'Not AI Letter','Test only not AI','2025-11-20 18:54:45',10,9,1,0),(37,'My AI Letter','Dear Ivan Jay,\n\nI hope this note finds you in good spirits. I’m writing to share a little piece of excitement that’s been on my mind lately. This is my first ever AI-generated letter, and I wanted to send it to you as a small token of the new ways we’re discovering to connect.\n\nIt feels a bit like stepping into a new chapter—one where words can be crafted with a touch of technology, yet still carry the warmth of a personal touch. I’ve always admired your kindness and your ability to make people feel heard, so I wanted this letter to reflect that same sincerity. Even though the words are generated, my intention is as genuine as ever: to let you know that you’re appreciated and that I’m grateful for the moments we’ve shared, whether in conversation, collaboration, or simply in the quiet exchange of ideas.\n\nI hope this letter brings a smile to your face and reminds you that, no matter how new the tools we use, the heart behind the message remains unchanged. Thank you for being a part of my journey, and for inspiring me to try new things—like this first AI-crafted note.\n\nWith sincere warmth and best wishes,\n\nIshy Rafols','2025-11-20 19:08:05',1,2,1,1),(38,'My AI Letter','Dear Ivan Jay,\n\nI hope this note finds you in good spirits. I’m writing to share a little piece of excitement that’s been on my mind lately. This is my first ever AI-generated letter, and I wanted to send it to you as a small token of the new ways we’re discovering to connect.\n\nIt feels a bit like stepping into a new chapter—one where words can be crafted with a touch of technology, yet still carry the warmth of a personal touch. I’ve always admired your kindness and your ability to make people feel heard, so I wanted this letter to reflect that same sincerity. Even though the words are generated, my intention is as genuine as ever: to let you know that you’re appreciated and that I’m grateful for the moments we’ve shared, whether in conversation, collaboration, or simply in the quiet exchange of ideas.\n\nI hope this letter brings a smile to your face and reminds you that, no matter how new the tools we use, the heart behind the message remains unchanged. Thank you for being a part of my journey, and for inspiring me to try new things—like this first AI-crafted note.\n\nWith sincere warmth and best wishes,\n\nIshy Rafols','2025-11-20 19:08:05',1,2,1,1),(39,'My AI Letter','Mahal kong Ivan Jay Adoptante,\n\nMagandang araw sa iyo, at sana’y ang iyong puso ay puno ng pag-asa habang binabasa mo ang liham na ito.\n\nMayroon akong isang napakagandang balita na nais kong ibahagi sa iyo—isang bagong web app na makakapagpabilis at magpapasaya sa iyong araw-araw na pagharap sa mga sulat at komunikasyon. Sa pamamagitan ng app na ito, maaari kang lumikha ng mga liham na puno ng damdamin nang madali at mabilis, gamit ang tulong ng AI para mas maging personal at makabuluhan ang iyong mensahe.\n\nSa simpleng paraan, ilahad mo lamang ang layunin ng sulat, ang tatanggap, at ilang mahahalagang punto na nais mong banggitin. Ang AI ay sasamahan ka sa pagbuo ng buong liham, na may tamang tono at istilo para sa iyo. Pagkatapos, madali mo na itong maipapasa o maipapadala sa pamamagitan ng email o anumang platform na iyong pinili.\n\nAng app na ito ay dinisenyo para maging simple at user‑friendly—kahit hindi ka teknikal, madali mo itong magagamit. Ang mahalaga ay nakatutulong ito sa iyo na mas maipahayag ang iyong damdamin at intensyon nang mas malinaw at mas maayos.\n\nSana’y masulit mo ang pagkakataong ito at makita kung paano nito mapapaigting ang iyong komunikasyon sa mga mahal mo sa buhay. Kung may anumang katanungan o kailangan mo ng tulong sa pag‑setup, huwag kang mag-atubiling magtanong—handang tumulong ako sa bawat hakbang.\n\nMaraming salamat sa iyong oras at pag-unawa. Nawa’y maging masaya at makabuluhan ang bawat liham na iyong isusulat sa paglipas ng araw.\n\nLubos na nagmamahal,\nLucius','2025-11-20 19:41:27',4,9,1,1),(40,'Ivan Jay Adoptante','Ako’y si Marie Therese Rafols, at ikaw ay si Ivan Jay Adoptante.  \nSa puso ng bawat hamon, tayo’y nagkakaisa bilang mga Power Rangers.','2025-11-21 15:33:55',10,12,1,1);
